WITH df2 AS (
  SELECT
    ym.CustomerID,
    ym.Consumption,
    c.Segment
  FROM yearmonth AS ym
  INNER JOIN customers AS c
    ON ym.CustomerID = c.CustomerID
  WHERE ym.Date BETWEEN '201301' AND '201312'
    AND c.Currency = 'CZK'
),
seg_min AS (
  SELECT
    Segment,
    MIN(Consumption) AS min_consumption
  FROM df2
  GROUP BY Segment
),
seg_min_customers AS (
  SELECT DISTINCT
    d.Segment,
    d.CustomerID
  FROM df2 AS d
  INNER JOIN seg_min AS m
    ON d.Segment = m.Segment
   AND d.Consumption = m.min_consumption
),
seg_totals AS (
  SELECT
    d.Segment,
    SUM(d.Consumption) AS total_consumption
  FROM df2 AS d
  GROUP BY d.Segment
),
seg_counts AS (
  SELECT
    Segment,
    COUNT(*) AS cnt_min_customers
  FROM seg_min_customers
  GROUP BY Segment
),
seg_avg AS (
  SELECT
    t.Segment,
    1.0 * t.total_consumption / c.cnt_min_customers AS annual_avg_consumption
  FROM seg_totals AS t
  INNER JOIN seg_counts AS c
    ON t.Segment = c.Segment
)
SELECT
  (sme.annual_avg_consumption - lam.annual_avg_consumption) AS diff_sme_minus_lam,
  (lam.annual_avg_consumption - kam.annual_avg_consumption) AS diff_lam_minus_kam,
  (kam.annual_avg_consumption - sme.annual_avg_consumption) AS diff_kam_minus_sme
FROM (SELECT annual_avg_consumption FROM seg_avg WHERE Segment = 'SME') AS sme
INNER JOIN (SELECT annual_avg_consumption FROM seg_avg WHERE Segment = 'LAM') AS lam
INNER JOIN (SELECT annual_avg_consumption FROM seg_avg WHERE Segment = 'KAM') AS kam;	----- bird -----	debit_card_specializing

  SELECT
    c.Segment,

    SUM(y.Consumption) AS total_consumption
  FROM yearmonth AS y

    ON y.CustomerID = c.CustomerID

    AND SUBSTR(y.Date, 1, 4) IN ('2012', '2013')

SELECT
  s.Segment,
  ((s.cons_2013 - s.cons_2012) * 100.0 / s.cons_2012) AS pct_increase
FROM (
  SELECT
    Segment,
    SUM(CASE WHEN yr = '2012' THEN total_consumption ELSE 0 END) AS cons_2012,
    SUM(CASE WHEN yr = '2013' THEN total_consumption ELSE 0 END) AS cons_2013
  FROM seg_year
  GROUP BY Segment
) AS s
WHERE s.cons_2012 <> 0
ORDER BY CASE s.Segment
  WHEN 'SME' THEN 1
  WHEN 'LAM' THEN 2
  WHEN 'KAM' THEN 3

END;	----- bird -----	debit_card_specializing
